trans-unit.source: Represents a visitor or rewriter for expression trees.
trans-unit.target: 代表運算式樹狀的造訪者或重寫器。

trans-unit.source: This class is designed to be inherited to create more specialized classes whose functionality requires traversing, examining or copying an expression tree.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別被為了繼承來建立更具特製化的類別，其功能需要周遊、 檢查或複製為運算式樹狀架構。
初始化 <see cref="T:System.Linq.Expressions.ExpressionVisitor" /> 的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Dispatches the expression or the list of expressions to one of the more specialized visit methods in this class.
trans-unit.target: 將運算式或運算式清單分派給此類別中較為特殊的其中一種造訪方法。

trans-unit.source: Dispatches the list of expressions to one of the more specialized visit methods in this class.
trans-unit.target: 將運算式清單分派給此類別中較為特殊的造訪方法之一。

trans-unit.source: The modified expression list, if any one of the elements were modified; otherwise, returns the original expression list.
trans-unit.target: 如果任何項目已經修改，則傳回修改的運算式清單，否則傳回原始運算式清單。

trans-unit.source: Dispatches the expression to one of the more specialized visit methods in this class.
trans-unit.target: 將運算式分派給此類別中較為特殊的造訪方法之一。

trans-unit.source: The modified expression, if it or any subexpression was modified; otherwise, returns the original expression.
trans-unit.target: 如果運算式本身或是任一子運算式已經修正，會傳回修正的運算式，否則傳回原始運算式。

trans-unit.source: A delegate that visits a single element, optionally replacing it with a new element.
trans-unit.target: 造訪單一項目的委派，並選擇性地將它取代為新項目。

trans-unit.source: Visits all nodes in the collection using a specified element visitor.
trans-unit.target: 使用特殊的項目造訪者，造訪集合中所有的節點。

trans-unit.source: The modified node list, if any of the elements were modified; otherwise, returns the original node list.
trans-unit.target: 如果任何項目已經修改，則傳回修改的節點清單，否則傳回原始節點清單。

trans-unit.source: Visits an expression, casting the result back to the original expression type.
trans-unit.target: 造訪運算式，並將結果轉換回原始運算式型別。

trans-unit.source: The name of the calling method; used to report to report a better error message.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫方法的名稱，用來回報較佳的錯誤訊息。

trans-unit.source: Visits all expressions in the collection, casting the results back to the original expression type.
trans-unit.target: 瀏覽集合中的運算式，並將結果轉換回原始運算式類型。

trans-unit.source: The modified expression collection, if any expression was modified; otherwise, returns the original expression collection.
trans-unit.target: 如果任一運算式已經修正，則會傳回修正的運算式集合，否則傳回原始運算式集合。

trans-unit.source: The visit method for one of the expressions returned a different type.
trans-unit.target: 其中一個運算式的瀏覽方法傳回不同的型別。

trans-unit.source: The name of the calling method; used to report to report a better error message.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫方法的名稱，用來回報較佳的錯誤訊息。

trans-unit.source: The visit method for this node returned a different type.

trans-unit.target: 造訪延伸運算式的子系。

trans-unit.source: This can be overridden to visit or rewrite specific extension nodes.
trans-unit.target: 這可以被覆寫，請瀏覽或重寫節點特定的副檔名。

trans-unit.source: If it is not overridden, this method will call <xref:System.Linq.Expressions.Expression.VisitChildren%2A>, which gives the node a chance to walk its children.
trans-unit.target: 如果未覆寫，會呼叫這個方法<xref:System.Linq.Expressions.Expression.VisitChildren%2A>，這可讓節點有機會查核其子系。

trans-unit.source: By default, <xref:System.Linq.Expressions.Expression.VisitChildren%2A> will try to reduce the node.
